.DT
drop
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
drop

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
drop -  The current value of the drop flag.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int drop(mixed dest)
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it is set, 0 if it is reset
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/move.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

The current value of the drop flag. This function is called by the
test_remove() function in the living object.  So it allows you to
move the object out of inanimate objects, just not out of the
players.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_drop(), reset_drop(), get()

.EP

